Instructions to run this project:
Please follow the below instructions to run the project:
Make sure you have python installed in your system and then open terminal to install django using below commands.
pip install django
move into the project directory where manage.py file exists
Open the terminal and run 
1)  python manage.py makemigrations RecipeApp
2)  python manage.py migrate

create super user for django admin panel where u can see the database
python manage.py createsuperuser
it will ask you for username,email and password in terminal
then run 
python manage.py runserver 
and open this url on chrome
for web app;
http://127.0.0.1:8000/

for admin panel
http://127.0.0.1:8000/admin
enter superuser username and password 
  

 
